-- ECB’s Asmussen Says Executive Board Needs One Voice, Welt Says
-- B y   C o r n e l i u s   R a h n
-- 2012-01-07T11:42:34Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2012-01-07/ecb-s-asmussen-says-executive-board-needs-one-voice-welt-says.html
European Central Bank Executive Board
member Joerg Asmussen said the six-member board he joined this
year needs to “be a team” and “act as one man vis-a-vis the
outside world,”  Welt am Sonntag  reported today, citing an
interview.  To contact the reporter on this story:
